title: So Undercover / Una Spia al Liceo (2012) with Miley Cyrus

sources.title: So Undercover / Una Spia al Liceo (2012) with Miley Cyrus
sources.description:
Teenager Molly works with her father, an ex-cop who has set up his own private investigator. A tough and cunning detective, Molly is hired by the FBI to infiltrate a college fraternity and keep an eye on the daughter of a crime boss who is about to testify against another criminal. Adjusting to life in the prestigious and refined university environment will prove more complicated for Molly than expected. But she will soon discover that appearances can be deceiving...

Original title: So Undercover
Alternative title: Una Spia al Liceo
Director: Tom Vaughan
Writers: Allan Loeb, Steven Pearl

Main cast:
Miley Cyrus - Molly Morris / Brook Stonebridge
Jeremy Piven - Armon Ranford
Mike O'Malley - Sam Morris
Josh Bowman - Nicholas Dexter
Lauren McKnight - Alex Patrone
Kelly Osbourne - Becky Slotsky
Eloise Mumford - Sasha Stolezinsky / Suzy Walters
Megan Park - Cotton Roberts
Alexis Knapp - Taylor Jaffe

Genres: Action, Adventure, Comedy, Crime, Drama, Mystery, Romance, Thriller
Release date: December 6, 2012 
Filming location: Alabama USA
